## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **metoclopramide black box 2009 (TD)** = 만성 1L gastroparesis 유일 FDA 약. tardive dyskinesia + extrapyramidal symptom 위험. 만성 use ≤12 weeks 권고. quantum-VQE 의 D2 CNS vs peripheral selectivity 가 직접 fit.
2. **relamorelin Phase 3 fail 2020 (Allergan/AbbVie)** = ghrelin agonist 만성 paradigm lessons. Phase 2b 양호 → Phase 3 primary endpoint fail. gastroparesis 임상 endpoint 의 difficulty (subjective symptom + delayed emptying disconnect).
3. **tradipitant (Vanda) NK1 antagonist** = 만성 paradigm gastroparesis Phase 3 ongoing. NK1 nausea/vomiting axis 가 prokinetic 외 alternative mechanism. FDA filing 2024 outcome open.
4. **prucalopride 2018** = 만성 5-HT4 selective — cisapride hERG-free successor. CIC indicated, gastroparesis off-label. selective 5-HT4 가 cardiac safety key.
5. **domperidone US 미승인 + EU/한국 approved** = D2 peripheral mAb-free + BBB-impermeant. cardiac arrhythmia (QT prolongation) FDA 우려로 IND only. 한국/EU 임상 routine.
6. **erythromycin tachyphylaxis** = 만성 motilin agonist 빠른 tolerance (2-4 weeks). abx scaffold non-selective. camicinal (GSK) non-abx motilin 시도 → discontinued.
7. **G-POEM 2013+** = 만성 endoscopic pyloromyotomy — RCT (POEMS 2024) refractory gastroparesis 양호 결과. drug-refractory 의 procedural alternative.
8. **Enterra gastric pacemaker (Medtronic) HDE 2000** = 만성 device — symptomatic 개선 mixed RCT. drug-refractory 적응증.
9. **K-mosapride + itopride + DA-9701 motilitone (Dong-A ST 2011)** = 한국 처방 routine — US 미승인. K-pharma 5-HT4 + D2 + AChE + herbal-derived multitarget. 식약처 framework + 산정특례 cross-link.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, gastroparesis 임상 의미 한정.

